deciding who to love forever. I am constantly decorating my bedroom with pictures of my two favourite handsome fiction men: Noah ( The Notebook) and Jean Valjean ( Les Miserables).

When I am not daydreaming about these guys, I am getting into adventures with my cousins – whom I love more than anything in this world – going to movies, having sleepovers, and eating as much chocolate as I possibly can. There are so many girls in this world who love reading, and I am thankful to your business for providing me with a safe place to explore my love for reading.

I would certainly recommend your business to a friend and I am looking forward to enjoying it a lot more in 2017!” – Paola #XmasBCWish #ILoveBCW
